txt.en: If you would like to skip the remainder of the  tutorial experience and be transported to Archet at the outset of the Blackwold incursion, speak with Postman Took again.
If you choose to skip the tutorial experience, you will be transported to Archet at the outset of the Blackwold incursion.\n\nAre you sure you want to continue?
Allows players to skip through to the public area of the game.
Talk to Postman Took to skip the Tutorial
If you would like to skip the remainder of the  tutorial experience and be transported to Archet at the outset of the Blackwold incursion, speak with Postman Took again.
